OL,3,CTUC leader urges Government to show it
OL,4,Cis on the side of workers
OL,6,FHe said TUC research shows significant
OL,7,Fsupport for a package of wealth taxes
OL,8,Fand taxes on financial institutions to
OL,9,Ffund public services and build a
OL,10,F"fairer" country.
OL,12,FIn an interview with the PA news
OL,13,Fagency ahead of the TUC Congress,
OL,14,Fwhich opens in Brighton on Sunday, Mr
OL,15,FNowak said Labour had inherited a
OL,16,F"toxic" legacy from the previous
OL,17,FConservative governments.
