OL,3,CTUC leader urges Government to show it
OL,4,Cis on the side of workers
OL,6,F"Public services have been decimated
OL,7,Fand Labour has a big job to rebuild
OL,8,Fthem," he said. "But Labour
OL,9,Fgovernments are best when they are
OL,10,Fambitious, and they should now prove
OL,11,Fthat every decision they make shows
OL,12,Fthey are on the side of working people.
OL,14,F"After more than a decade of Tory
OL,15,Fneglect, this country is crying out
OL,16,Ffor investment ` in our schools, NHS
OL,17,Fand local services.
