OL,3,CTUC leader urges Government to show it
OL,4,Cis on the side of workers
OL,6,F"The public overwhelmingly want
OL,7,Finvestment to deliver better services
OL,8,Fright across the country ` whether
OL,9,Fit's cutting NHS waiting lists so
OL,10,Fpatients can get the prompt treatment
OL,11,Fthey need or funding schools so our
OL,12,Fkids have the right books and
OL,13,Fresources.
OL,15,F"They want fair taxes too. People have
OL,16,Fhad it with a system where those with
OL,17,Fthe broadest shoulders don't pull
OL,18,Ftheir weight.
