OL,3,CTUC leader urges Government to show it
OL,4,Cis on the side of workers
OL,6,FThe TUC poll of more than 5,000 adults
OL,7,Fshowed four out of five support a
OL,8,Fwealth tax package to help cut the NHS
OL,9,Fwaiting list and to ensure schools
OL,10,Fhave enough money for textbooks,
OL,11,Fequipment and basic repairs.
OL,13,FThe union organisation said it
OL,14,Fbelieves voters would reward the
OL,15,FGovernment if investment in public
OL,16,Fservices was funded by wealth taxes.
